basics.summary: I am a recent graduate of The University of Massachusetts Amherst Isenberg School of Managment. I have a Bachelors in Operations and Information Managment with a certificate in Bussiness Analytics. I studied at The University of Hawaii at Manoa in the fall 2021. I used Java Script as well as Json over the course of my final semster of undergrad to create an E-commerce webite I am very proud of. Please check it out in my essays!
